Pre-Game Insights: Scotland and Australia will lock horns in the 1st T20I of Australia tour of Scotland 2024 on Wednesday, 4 September 2024, at Grange Cricket Club, Edinburgh.
Scotland is ranked 13th, while Australia holds the second spot in the ICC T20I rankings.
This series will be Australia’s first visit to Scotland since 2013 and their first assignment after the T20 World Cup.
Scotland, hosting the series, will be keen to showcase their prowess on home soil.
Australia, known for their aggressive and disciplined approach, will be looking to start the series on a high note.
